subject: Olympic Games (2010)
Olympic Games
Ski Jumping
Women and Girls
lead_paragraph: Of the 20 forerunners who ensure conditions are optimal for competitors, two are women, rankling other elite female ski jumpers who have fought the Olympic ban.
